{"tid":2321006,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"蘋果日報：傳京訪民持手榴彈威脅炸橋 狙擊手戒備 網民：多大冤屈才走這絕路","createTime":"2020-12-11T08:21:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-11T09:38:32.000Z","uid":290404,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"fe5a954f1a8b4c48b2d7dcac136d143017f0961e","tid":2321006,"uid":290404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T08:21:47.000Z","msg":"北京在昨日「國際人權日」，發生疑似訪民聲稱要炸橋事件。事發於國家信訪局和人社局附近的北京南二環陶然橋，一名老年男子，手持一個類似手榴彈的物體，欲前往國家信訪局，卻被大批警察包圍在馬路中央，狙擊手更一度奉召到場戒備，該名男子最後被拘捕。不過，北京官方未就事件作出回應，內媒亦未見有報道。網民則評論說：「多大的冤屈才讓人走這樣的絕路呢？今天（昨日）是國際人權日，人權在中國就是一個笑話！」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201211/2ZVVWTKVF5HXXO57W5S72VIVRA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201211%2F2ZVVWTKVF5HXXO57W5S72VIVRA%2F&d=gjdgNhcllSDI%2FgTZdT0hmp6X7PLg0GRX82CuX%2BG2FI0%3D&h=25b19dff\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201211%2F2ZVVWTKVF5HXXO57W5S72VIVRA%2F&h=2ae794c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201211/2ZVVWTKVF5HXXO57W5S72VIVRA/</a>"},{"pid":"88b25e10718c5ff32ab633d9a30a6eb78061dd9f","tid":2321006,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T08:22:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dc1b03782c4de14de6f83da9f07c10abaa83124","tid":2321006,"uid":224510,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T08:24:01.000Z","msg":"又屈佢恐怖份子㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"973b00d22df05024b6532cc0cae700013fe67e2e","tid":2321006,"uid":301989,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy